\f0\i\b \cf0 Mode of participating and changing\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0\b0 \cf0 One of the undeniable powers of play and games lies in their ability to make us take part in something, focusing all our attention. But the player does not participate just \'93bodily\'94. When playing, we make constant conscious decisions that define the course of action and the destiny of the game. But, when we play, it is not just our actions which affect the complex ludic ecosystem. Our actions and the structure of play sometimes manage to change the player\'92s awareness and how they see the world. By placing ourselves in the position of others, the digital games in this area propose different modes of changing perspective, perception and awareness about certain social, cultural and existential conditions. \
